		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV>Clerics have the slowest mana regen of any caster, and even of many hybrids. Currently with full mana regen from items and AA (23), C6, and sitting, it takes me 14.8 minutes to go from OOM to FM.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I think 1/4 of an hour to regen is not just too long, it is damned STOOPID!!</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>A few months back some dev said they were "looking into it". Since then I have heard nothing.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>So what ever happened to the mana regen issue?</DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							70 Cleric (<a href="http://eqplayers.station.sony.com/character_profile.vm?characterId=571230694339">The Pink Elf</a>) (854AA)<br>60 <a href="http://eqplayers.station.sony.com/character_profile.vm?characterId=571230973715">Warrior</a><br>70 <a href="http://eqplayers.station.sony.com/character_profile.vm?characterId=571231102724">Enchanter</a> (73 AA)<br>28 <a href="http://eqplayers.station.sony.com/character_profile.vm?characterId=571231473446">Ranger</a> fun gimp<br><br>Viking Alliance (Stromm)
							</div>
								
