			20(c6)+23(ft)+3(mc)+24(sitting)+9(AotP)=79 mana per tic.<br><br>14.8 minutes is 148 tics.<br><br>Thats an 11692 mana pool, not counting clickys (Even the Phylactery adds another 296 mana).  I'm sure its a problem high-end, but youre not the lowest of all casters.  Enchanters dont have AotP.  Yes, they have Gather Mana, and its on a long recycle time.  I dont see them giving Gather Mana to clerics, as that would basically mean you have twice the clerics for long duration encounters (yes I know, its not really twice since you arent casting heals twice as fast, but you do have twice the mana pool).  Maybe Gather Mana with a 30 second stun, or some other debuff.. /shrug.  But its not as easy as just plopping down more mana regen for clerics, especially with the problem only being in the high end.  A Gather Mana equivilant would also hit the low end.	
