<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>
<HR>
</P>
<P>Thaere wrote:</P>
<P>Fact is EVERY caster class has this problem.&nbsp; IMO the best solution is to remodel the mana regen rates like the health regen rates - if you sit down and wait, the rate increases steadily.&nbsp; Same goes for endurance.<BR>
<HR>
</P></BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>That would be the simplest short term solution and would at least solve some of the current problems - and it should also be easy to implement.</P>
<P>However, for a long term fix SOE should go back and look at ALL regen rates for ALL classes, and perhaps start over from the ground up. That is probably easier said than done though, as in many cases the devs would be working with 6 to 8 year old code that would give spaghetti a bad name.</FONT><BR></P>
